Depends: R (>= 4.3.0), methods, BiocGenerics, S4Vectors, IRanges,
	GenomeInfoDb (>= 1.33.17), Biostrings, BSgenome
Imports: utils, stats, Biobase, rtracklayer
Suggests: GenomicRanges, GenomicFeatures, testthat, knitr, rmarkdown,
         BiocStyle, devtools
